{"tid":1883283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"占士邦電影《007：生死有時》取消中國宣傳「現在不是死的時候」","createTime":"2020-02-16T23:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T00:18:01.000Z","uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85fafee0e6eebbde1c1677a1254491ac84eb9d9f","tid":1883283,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T23:36:17.000Z","msg":"丹尼爾格力（Daniel Craig）主演的占士邦電影《007：生死有時》（No Time To Die）將於4月公映，今次是丹尼爾最後一次飾演特務占士邦，特別叫人期待。不過由於新冠肺炎在中國肆虐，占士邦也要投降，電影公司決定取消中國宣傳，大陸影迷無緣見到丹尼爾與拍檔們的風采！英國傳媒《泰晤士報》非常抵死，於標題玩戲名食字，指占士邦因為新冠肺炎取消去北京是因為「現在不是死的時候」（because this is no time to die）。"},{"pid":"ed5c498d78f5b7e58d0e8b0db1d7426f6338f9aa","tid":1883283,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:04:05.000Z","msg":"No die No RMB"},{"pid":"178d75c9d8fc488440054dd096bfca163138869c","tid":1883283,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:06:15.000Z","msg":"擇日再死"},{"pid":"52fa31c44515edcf09a13cf91bf2559808ddc6c5","tid":1883283,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:07:53.000Z","msg":"睇完007 ff下昔日英國幾型<br />\n<br />\n而家英國跪係度啜維尼屎眼"},{"pid":"8db2208ac3e0f20e98fda3c3572947ade595f2c4","tid":1883283,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"178d75c9d8fc488440054dd096bfca163138869c","tid":1883283,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:06:15.000Z","msg":"擇日再死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"睇完先死"},{"pid":"473e81110213a9c726edf3d37f7128cbb97f394e","tid":1883283,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:18:01.000Z","msg":"都入戲院想睇😷"}]}